This Code made for cleansing abusive words and slangs terms.

Which the data orinally from https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ilhamfp31/indonesian-abusive-and-hate-speech-twitter-text.
Muhammad Okky Ibrohim and Indra Budi. 2019. Multi-label Hate Speech and Abusive Language Detection in Indonesian Twitter. In ALW3: 3rd Workshop on Abusive Language Online, 46-57.

Using swagger to documented the api and python as programming language.
The api input can be text or file uploaded with extension csv.
The API method use here are GET, POST, PUT, DELETE
